definitions.definition: ( derogatory , slang ) A quirky , silly or stupid , socially inept person, or one who is out of touch with contemporary trends and typically has unfashionable hobbies. (Overlaps conceptually with nerd and geek , but does not imply the same level of intelligence.) [from the 20th c.]
( vulgar , slang ) The penis . [from the 20th c.]
